parameters.name: YEARDOY
parameters.description:
Year and day of year of periapsis, S/C event time, UT (e.g. 78340 is day
      340 of year 1978, Jan 1 = day 1).

parameters.name: SECOFDAYOFPERIAPSIS
parameters.description:
Second of day of periapsis, S/C event time, UT. This value can be less  
      than zero or greater than 86,400 if periapsis falls within 1.5 hours of 
      midnight.

parameters.name: DENSITY
parameters.description: Log10 of the number density of electrons (Ne)
